bio: Dr. James Anderson is a board-certified cardiologist with over 15 years of experience in treating heart conditions. He specializes in preventive cardiology and cardiac rehabilitation.
Dr. Maria Garcia is a licensed psychiatrist specializing in anxiety disorders, depression, and mood disorders. She provides compassionate care with evidence-based treatments.
Dr. Robert Taylor is an orthopedic surgeon with expertise in sports medicine and joint replacement. He has performed over 1000 successful surgeries.
Dr. Lisa Brown is a pediatrician dedicated to providing comprehensive healthcare for children from infancy through adolescence. She focuses on preventive care and early intervention.
Dr. Thomas Martinez is a dermatologist specializing in medical and cosmetic dermatology. He treats a wide range of skin conditions and offers advanced treatment options.
